\"everything\", \"from\": 935, \"to\": 945}, {\"ngram\": \"my career\", \"from\": 967, \"to\": 976}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I know how much it meant for everyone there.\", \"from\": 1005, \"to\": 1050, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 1035, \"to\": 1043}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am getting emotional because I am proud, not sad.\\\"\", \"from\": 1051, \"to\": 1103, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Duffy showed every ounce of her experience and know-how to navigate a Seine River under scrutiny for its pollution levels, leading the race after the 1,500-kilometre swim and the first lap of the 40km bike.\", \"from\": 1105, \"to\": 1311, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Duffy\", \"from\": 1105, \"to\": 1110}, {\"ngram\": \"every ounce\", \"from\": 1118, \"to\": 1129}, {\"ngram\": \"her experience\", \"from\": 1133, \"to\": 1147}, {\"ngram\": \"a Seine River\", \"from\": 1173, \"to\": 1186}, {\"ngram\": \"scrutiny\", \"from\": 1193, \"to\": 1201}, {\"ngram\": \"its pollution levels\", \"from\": 1206, \"to\": 1226}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 1236, \"to\": 1244}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1,500-kilometre swim\", \"from\": 1251, \"to\": 1275}, {\"ngram\": \"the first lap\", \"from\": 1280, \"to\": 1293}, {\"ngram\": \"the 40km bike\", \"from\": 1297, \"to\": 1310}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was her first proper feel for the Seine, having missed the Paris Test Event last year through injury, and given the cancelled sessions because of the quality of the water on Sunday and Monday when the men's race was postponed.\", \"from\": 1313, \"to\": 1542, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1350, \"end\": 1355, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999990923243, \"rank\": 9.075772477147752e-10, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her 