": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"rivers\", \"from\": 1826, \"to\": 1832}, {\"ngram\": \"currents\", \"from\": 1837, \"to\": 1845}, {\"ngram\": \"his paddling background\", \"from\": 1851, \"to\": 1874}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I got to the first buoy, and I was second, and I could tell the person in front of me wasn't swimming particularly fast.\", \"from\": 1877, \"to\": 1998, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first buoy\", \"from\": 1887, \"to\": 1901}, {\"ngram\": \"the person\", \"from\": 1938, \"to\": 1948}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 1952, \"to\": 1957}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I thought, 'I will just take it, and swim strategically as best I can.\", \"from\": 2000, \"to\": 2071, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That opened up a big gap because others were not swimming the current very smart.\\\"\", \"from\": 2072, \"to\": 2154, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a big gap\", \"from\": 2087, \"to\": 2096}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 2105, \"to\": 2111}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Having rolled back the years in the swim, Duffy continued to power off solo on the slick cobbles of the iconic Champ-Elys\\u00e9es, leading 17 seconds at one point before being pegged back by the chase group.\", \"from\": 2156, \"to\": 2358, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2198, \"end\": 2203, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francis_P._Duffy\", \"score\": 0.8016571480210545, \"rank\": 0.1527333258329899, \"text\": \"Duffy\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francis_P._Duffy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francis_P._Duffy\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the years\", \"from\": 2175, \"to\": 2184}, {\"ngram\": \"the swim\", \"from\": 2188, \"to\": 2196}, {\"ngram\": \"the slick cobbles\", \"from\": 2235, \"to\": 2252}, {\"ngram\": \"the iconic Champ-Elys\\u00e9es\", \"from\": 2256, \"to\": 2280}, {\"ngram\": \"17 seconds\", \"from\": 2290, \"to\": 2300}, {\"ngram\": \"one point\", \"from\": 2304, \"to\": 2313}, {\"ngram\": \"the chase group\", \"from\": 2342, \"to\": 2357}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"[Leading the bike] left me with a bit of a dilemma on the bike,\\\" said Duffy, who only returned to competitive action in May after a lengthy knee injury.\", \"from\": 2360, \"to\": 2513, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2431, \"end\": 2436, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francis_P._Duffy\", \"score\": 0.8016571480210545, \"rank\": 0.1527333258329899, \"text\": \"Duffy\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francis_P._Duffy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francis_P._Duffy\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the bike\", \"from\": 2370, \"to\": 2378}, {\"ngram\": \"a bit\", \"from\": 2393, \"to\": 2398}, {\"ngram\": \"a dilemma\", \"from\": 2402, \"to\": 2411}, {\"ngram\": \"the bike\", \"from\": 2415, \"to\": 2423}, {\"ngram\": \"competitive action\", \"from\": 2459, \"to\": 2477}, {\"ngram\": \"May\", \"from\": 2481, \"to\": 2484}, {\"ngram\": \"a lengthy knee injury\", \"from\": 2491, \"to\": 2512}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I thought, wow, maybe I will just go for it!\", \"from\": 2515, \"to\": 2560, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But there were strong girls, and no one leaves me out there, they know they can not.\", \"from\": 2561, \"to\": 2645, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"strong girls\", \"from\": 2576, \"to\": 2588}, {\"ngram\": \"no one\", \"from\": 2594, \"to\": 2600}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I just tried to make it a bit aggressive.\\\"\", \"from\": 2647, \"to\": 2690, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Duffy continued to dig deep in the 10km run, but by the end of the first lap, a second successive Olympic medal had slipped her by.\", \"from\": 2692, \"to\": 2823, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Duffy\", \"from\": 2692, \"to\": 2697}, {\"ngram\": \"the 10km run\", \"from\": 2723, \"to\": 2735}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 2744, \"to\": 2751}, {\"ngram\": \"the first lap\", \"from\": 2755, \"to\": 2768}, {\"ngram\": \"a second successive Olympic medal\", \"from\": 2770, \"to\": 2803}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I just did not have my run legs today, which is really disappointing,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2825, \"to\": 2906, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my run legs\", \"from\": 2846, \"to\": 2857}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have been running much better than that and know I can run with the leaders.\", \"from\": 2908, \"to\": 2987, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the leaders\", \"from\": 2975, \"to\": 2986}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's racing, though.\", \"from\": 2988, \"to\": 3010, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Honestly, even earlier this year in April, it was doubtful I would get here.\", \"from\": 3012, \"to\": 3089, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"April\", \"from\": 3049, \"to\": 3054}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So, to be here in the mix and finish fifth at my fifth Olympics - I can be very proud.\", \"from\": 3090, \"to\": 3176, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the mix\", \"from\": 3108, \"to\": 3115}, {\"ngram\": \"my fifth Olympics\", \"from\": 3136, \"to\": 3153}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am a competitor, of course, and wanted to be on that podium, and I knew I could run to be on it.\", \"from\": 3178, \"to\": 3277, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a competitor\", \"from\": 3184, \"to\": 3196}, {\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 3201, \"to\": 3207}, {\"ngram\": \"that podium\", \"from\": 3229, \"to\": 3240}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a little bittersweet right now, but I think, with time, I will be very proud of my finish.\\\"\", \"from\": 3278, \"to\": 3374, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 3333, \"to\": 3337}, {\"ngram\": \"my finish\", \"from\": 3363, \"to\": 3372}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her Olympic chapter might be over, but Duffy said she has no intention of retiring yet.\", \"from\": 3376, \"to\": 3463, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3415, \"end\": 3420, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francis_P._Duffy\", \"score\": 0.8016571480210545, \"rank\": 0.1527333258329899, \"text\": \"Duffy\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francis_P._Duffy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francis_P._Duffy\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her Olympic chapter\", \"from\": 3376, \"to\": 3395}, {\"ngram\": \"no intention\", \"from\": 3434, \"to\": 3446}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am going to do some longer-course racing,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 3465, \"to\": 3521, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some longer-course racing\", \"from\": 3483, \"to\": 3508}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not know how many other short course races I will do.\", \"from\": 3522, \"to\": 3581, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"how many other short course races\", \"from\": 3537, \"to\": 3570}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have accomplished everything I have wanted to.\", \"from\": 3583, \"to\": 3632, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 3604, \"to\": 3614}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am pretty happy with how it's gone.\\\"\", \"from\": 3633, \"to\": 3671, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"France's Cassandre Beaugrand claimed the victory in front of her home crowd in 1:54:55.\", \"from\": 3673, \"to\": 3760, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3673, \"end\": 3679, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.5036972957815984, \"rank\": 0.5538159835457402, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 3682, \"end\": 3701, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cassandre_Beaugrand\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cassandre Beaugrand\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cassandre_Beaugrand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cassandre_Beaugrand\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the victory\", \"from\": 3710, \"to\": 3721}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 3725, \"to\": 3730}, {\"ngram\": \"her home crowd\", \"from\": 3734, \"to\": 3748}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bernews will be providing comprehensive coverage of Bermuda's athletes in the coming weeks, #2024Olympics#Bermuda2024#FloraDuffy#Olympics#StephenWrightReports Category:All,News,Sports Trackback URL|Comments RSS Feed Was an epic race, the swim was crazy and an amazing performance from Flora.\", \"from\": 3764, \"to\": 4059, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3816, \"end\": 3823, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bermuda\", \"score\": 0.9999999632227634, \"rank\": 3.2956752619027714e-08, \"text\": \"Bermuda\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bermuda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bermuda\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Bernews\", \"from\": 3764, \"to\": 3771}, {\"ngram\": \"comprehensive coverage\", \"from\": 3790, \"to\": 3812}, {\"ngram\": \"the coming weeks\", \"from\": 3838, \"to\": 3854}, {\"ngram\": \"#2024Olympics#Bermuda2024#FloraDuffy#Olympics#StephenWrightReports Category\", \"from\": 3856, \"to\": 3931}, {\"ngram\": \"News\", \"from\": 3936, \"to\": 3940}, {\"ngram\": \"Sports Trackback URL|Comments RSS Feed\", \"from\": 3941, \"to\": 3979}, {\"ngram\": \"an epic race\", \"from\": 3984, \"to\": 3996}, {\"ngram\": \"the swim\", \"from\": 3998, \"to\": 4006}, {\"ngram\": \"an amazing performance\", \"from\": 4021, \"to\": 4043}, {\"ngram\": \"Flora\", \"from\": 4049, \"to\": 4054}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Given the fast long straight and relatively flat sections on the bike it was impossible to break and not be caught by a working together chase group.\", \"from\": 4060, \"to\": 4209, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the fast long straight and relatively flat sections\", \"from\": 4066, \"to\": 4117}, {\"ngram\": \"the bike\", \"from\": 4121, \"to\": 4129}, {\"ngram\": \"a working together chase group\", \"from\": 4178, \"to\": 4208}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If there had been someone with her away from the top contenders Flora would have definately been on podium, if not won it.\", \"from\": 4210, \"to\": 4332, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 4228, \"to\": 4235}, {\"ngram\": \"the top contenders\", \"from\": 4255, \"to\": 4273}, {\"ngram\": \"Flora\", \"from\": 4274, \"to\": 4279}, {\"ngram\": \"podium\", \"from\": 4310, \"to\": 4316}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The leaders group needed pushing and Flora did more than her fair share on the front pulling them along\\u2026.pretty sure more than the other main contenders, when it may have been a better tactic to draft until nearing transition.\", \"from\": 4334, \"to\": 4560, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The leaders group\", \"from\": 4334, \"to\": 4351}, {\"ngram\": \"Flora\", \"from\": 4371, \"to\": 4376}, {\"ngram\": \"her fair share\", \"from\": 4391, \"to\": 4405}, {\"ngram\": \"the front\", \"from\": 4409, \"to\": 4418}, {\"ngram\": \"the other main contenders\", \"from\": 4461, \"to\": 4486}, {\"ngram\": \"a better tactic\", \"from\": 4510, \"to\": 4525}, {\"ngram\": \"transition\", \"from\": 4549, \"to\": 4559}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That would have run the risk of a chase group catching though, so a double edged sword.\", \"from\": 4561, \"to\": 4648, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the risk\", \"from\": 4581, \"to\": 4589}, {\"ngram\": \"a chase group\", \"from\": 4593, \"to\": 4606}, {\"ngram\": \"a double edged sword\", \"from\": 4627, \"to\": 4647}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thought, given the conditions with all the crashes during the race, the crazy before the horn starts from a bunch off the pontoon, the mad flow and drift of the river, coming back from injuries and more, Flora was excellent !\", \"from\": 4650, \"to\": 4875, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the conditions\", \"from\": 4665, \"to\": 4679}, {\"ngram\": \"all the crashes\", \"from\": 4685, \"to\": 4700}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 4708, \"to\": 4716}, {\"ngram\": \"the horn\", \"from\": 4735, \"to\": 4743}, {\"ngram\": \"a bunch\", \"from\": 4756, \"to\": 4763}, {\"ngram\": \"the pontoon\", \"from\": 4768, \"to\": 4779}, {\"ngram\": \"the mad flow\", \"from\": 4781, \"to\": 4793}, {\"ngram\": \"drift\", \"from\": 4798, \"to\": 4803}, {\"ngram\": \"the river\", \"from\": 4807, \"to\": 4816}, {\"ngram\": \"injuries\", \"from\": 4835, \"to\": 4843}, {\"ngram\": \"Flora\", \"from\": 4854, \"to\": 4859}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thank you Flora not just for what you accomplished over the years at the olympics, but for having our Country, Bermuda, being put in peoples minds over and over and over again with your smile passion and enthusiasm.\", \"from\": 4876, \"to\": 5092, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4987, \"end\": 4994, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bermuda\", \"score\": 0.9999999632227634, \"rank\": 3.2956752619027714e-08, \"text\": \"Bermuda\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bermuda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bermuda\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the years\", \"from\": 4932, \"to\": 4941}, {\"ngram\": \"the olympics\", \"from\": 4945, \"to\": 4957}, {\"ngram\": \"our Country\", \"from\": 4974, \"to\": 4985}, {\"ngram\": \"peoples minds\", \"from\": 5009, \"to\": 5022}, {\"ngram\": \"your smile passion\", \"from\": 5057, \"to\": 5075}, {\"ngram\": \"enthusiasm\", \"from\": 5080, \"to\": 5090}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Good luck on your next challenge.\", \"from\": 5094, \"to\": 5127, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Good luck\", \"from\": 50